casebody.data:
Jose Susumo AZANO MATSURA, Petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 19-568 Supreme Court of the United States. Feb. 24, 2020

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit for further consideration in light of Rehaif v. United States , 588 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 2191, 204 L.Ed.2d 594 (2019).
